import React from 'react';
import { View, ScrollView, Image, TextInput, Text} from 'react-native';

import css from "./Style"
import global from "../Global/Style"
import { Feather } from '@expo/vector-icons';

export default function CadastrarAssistido({navigation}){
    return(
        <View style={global.body}>
            <Image style={css.image} source={require("../assets/logo.png")}/>
            <View style={css.scrollView}>
                <ScrollView>
                    <Text style={css.title}>Assistido</Text>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Nome..." place style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Nome social..." place style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="RG..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="CPF..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Sexo..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Nascimento..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Estado civil..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Naturalidade..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Cartão cidadão..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Cartão do SUS..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <View style={{width:150,
                        height:150,
                        backgroundColor: "#C4C4C4",
                        alignItems: "center",
                        justifyContent: "center",
                        alignSelf: "center",
                        marginTop: "5%"}}>
                        <Text>Foto</Text>
                    </View>
                    <View style={{
                        width: 200,
                        height: 100,
                        flexDirection: "column",
                        alignItems: "center",
                        justifyContent: "center",
                        alignSelf: "center"}}>
                        <Feather name="camera" size={24} color="blue" />
                        <Text style={{color: "blue"}}>Adicionar foto</Text>
                    </View>
                    <Text style={{color: "black",
                    fontSize:20,
                    alignSelf: "center",
                    fontWeight: "bold",
                    marginTop: "10%"}}>Familiar</Text>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Nome..." place style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Parentesco..." place style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Telefone..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="E-mail..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <TextInput placeholder="Endereço..." style={css.info}></TextInput>
                    <Text style={{
                        color:"blue",
                        fontSize: 20,
                        fontWeight: "bold",
                        alignSelf: "center",
                        marginTop: "5%"}}>Salvar</Text>
                </ScrollView>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}
